## Vision

> Build a scraper that crawls through multiple data sources and presents data to frontline workers in a much more efficient way.

---

## Solution Overview (Option B — EC2 + S3 + Postgres)

A sophisticated, cloud-based solution hosted entirely on AWS with a dedicated EC2 instance handling scraping, UI, and database. No additional on-premise infrastructure or maintenance required.

| Attribute | Details |
|---|---|
| **Hosting** | AWS |
| **Setup** | Cloud-based; no additional infra or maintenance needed |
| **Integrations** | All AWS-based — minimal integration overhead |
| **Sustainability** | Scalable as needed |
| **Accessibility** | Any device with internet connection |
| **End-user Flexibility** | Flexible data presentation |
| **Permission / Export** | Download data by selection: CSV / PDF / Checklist |
| **Support** | AWS shared support for infra; own team support for data |

